00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.200
Under the Network icon, you can view all members.

2
00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:06.160
Click Contact Member to send messages.

3
00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:10.160
Don't worry, this does not share any of your personal information.

4
00:00:10.160 --> 00:00:15.440
Chat with crew members about upcoming jobs, ask higher roles for guidance or advice,

5
00:00:15.440 --> 00:00:18.000
and connect with local crew leads for courses.

6
00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:23.040
Traveling? Find and connect with members in your destination.

7
00:00:23.040 --> 00:00:27.120
Networking helps build strong teams, gain knowledge,

8
00:00:27.120 --> 00:00:31.120
and advance your career into higher roles with higher pay.

9
00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:35.840
This is also where you can find a member's rating and overall score.

10
00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:37.520
You can rate members here too.

11
00:00:37.520 --> 00:00:41.200
Just click on Rating, then click Write a review.

12
00:00:41.760 --> 00:00:45.040
You will add a star review and a comment on why.

13
00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:46.960
Then click Submit.

14
00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:56.960
This rating and review now shows up for all members to see.
